5. Notices and Amendments
In order to provide you with better service, our business will change from time to time, and this Privacy Policy will also be adjusted accordingly. We will remind you of relevant content updates by sending an updated version on our mobile terminal, and please visit us to keep abreast of the latest privacy terms. Under the foregoing circumstances, if you continue to use our services, you agree to accept and be bound by the revised terms.

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or your personal information or privacy when using our services, please contact our customer service with a full description, and we will try our best to resolve it.
